column3:
Flare pendant are a beautiful example of fine craftsmanship and attention to detail. The first edition pendant features a 6mm deep purple amethyst gemstone at its center, with two 3mm amethyst gemstones on either side, creating a balanced and elegant design. The pendants are made from sterling silver and measures 1 1/5" x 3/5". Hand-carved and cast in sterling silver, this pendant is a true work of art.

Flare penants act as a versatile accessory that can be worn for any occasion, whether it's a night out on the town or a casual brunch with friends. It is a unique and one-of-a-kind piece, as it the first edition run of this wax carving. Jacob Critter Engel handcrafted this pendant in 2021, using only the highest quality materials. Flare pendants are a timeless piece of jewelry that will be treasured for years to come, and would make a thoughtful and unique gift for someone special.

This beautiful 0.54 carat Purple Winza Sapphire displays a deep, rich purple hue that is both regal and sophisticated. The gemstone has been expertly cut in a shield cut by Michael Sdz Morabito, a highly skilled gem cutter who is known for his precision and attention to detail. This unique gemstone is sure to add a touch of elegance to any jewelry design.

 

Gemstone Weight: 0.54 carats

Color: Purple

Origin: Winza, Tanzania

Species: Sapphire

Cut By: Michael Sdz Morabito

Cut: Shield Cut

 

Disclaimer:

When you purchase this gemstone, you are taking the first step towards starting a custom order. This can serve as confirmation of a previously discussed custom order, or as a way to reserve the gemstone that you love and don't want to miss out on. If you do not plan to have the gemstone set with us at [efd], it can be shipped to you upon request. We appreciate your business and look forward to working with you to create a one-of-a-kind piece of jewelry.

Introducing our stunning Paprok Tourmaline wrapped in a combination of sterling silver and 14/20 gold-filled wire. This exquisite piece is meticulously handcrafted with attention to detail and the utmost care. The Paprok Tourmaline is known for its beautiful range of colors and unique properties that make it a favorite of many gemstone enthusiasts.

Whether you're looking for a special gift for a loved one or a unique piece to add to your collection, this Paprok Tourmaline pendant is sure to impress. Don't miss out on this one-of-a-kind piece and take advantage of our promotion today.

Crafted to perfection, our 13 Point Bolts are the perfect addition to your jewelry collection. Hand carved in wax and then cast in sterling silver, these unique bolts boast 13 points and can be customized with the gemstone of your choice. Perfect for a special gift or a personal accessory, these bolts are sure to make a statement.

With our special code 'FREECHAIN', you can get a 1.8mm half-round sterling silver box chain for free. Order now to get your own 13 Point Bolt – but remember, each item is made to order, so your order will spend 3-5 days in production before being shipped.

Introducing our unique Striker Sterling Silver Pendant, available with your choice of gemstone. The intricate striker design was originally carved in wax, then cast in sterling silver using traditional techniques. The result is a beautiful and highly detailed piece that is sure to turn heads.

Whether you're looking for a special gift for a loved one or a unique piece to add to your collection, this Striker Sterling Silver Pendant is sure to impress. Each piece is made by hand with attention to detail and the utmost care, ensuring that you receive a truly one-of-a-kind piece.

Introducing Primum Aurum - my first solid gold creation! This stunning ring was hand fabricated in November 2022 and is available in size 7 (can be sized). Primum Aurum features a 14k yellow gold cathedral band, 14k yellow and white gold custom head, and a breathtaking 1.24ct Sea Foam Green Montana Sapphire cut by Michael Morabito. Make a statement with this unique and beautiful ring!

Size: 7 (can be sized)

Featuring:

-14k YG Cathedral Band

-14k YG & WG Custom Head

-1.24ct Sea Foam Green Montana Sapphire cut by Michael Morabito

Introducing Incrumentum – a magnificent pendant crafted through five years of devotion to jewelry making. It boasts of a 925 sterling silver frame, settings, and filigree, 10k yellow gold ornate beads, 14k gold-filled wire honeycomb, a 1ct Mexican fire opal, a 3mm tourmaline, two 2mm tourmalines, two 2mm citrines, two 2mm hessonite garnets, and a genuine G/H SI2-SI3 diamond. The combination of materials creates a breathtaking piece that's sure to make a statement.
